Introduction

Base URL: http://example-test.laravel.com

This documentation aims to provide all the information you need to work with our API.

As you scroll, you'll see code examples for working with the API in different programming languages in the dark area to the right (or as part of the content on mobile). You can switch the language used with the tabs at the top right (or from the nav menu at the top left on mobile).

Authenticating requests

This API is authenticated using a Bearer token.

Send your token in the Authorization header:

Authorization: Bearer <token>

You can retrieve the token by calling the login endpoint (POST /api/login).

Endpoints

用户登录接口

Example request:
curl --request POST \
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/login" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json" \
    --data "{
    \"email\": \"user@example.com\",
    \"password\": \"password123\"
}"

const url = new URL(
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/login"
);

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "email": "user@example.com",
    "password": "password123"
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());
Received response:
Request failed with error:


Tip: Check that you're properly connected to the network.
If you're a maintainer of ths API, verify that your API is running and you've enabled CORS.
You can check the Dev Tools console for debugging information.

Request      

POST api/login

Headers

Content-Type      

Example: application/json

Accept      

Example: application/json

Body Parameters

email   string   

用户邮箱 Example: user@example.com

password   string   

用户密码 Example: password123

用户登出接口

requires authentication

Example request:
curl --request POST \
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/logout" \
    --header "Authorization: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json"
const url = new URL(
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/logout"
);

const headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());
Received response:
Request failed with error:


Tip: Check that you're properly connected to the network.
If you're a maintainer of ths API, verify that your API is running and you've enabled CORS.
You can check the Dev Tools console for debugging information.

requires authentication

Example request:

    --get "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/me" \
    --header "Authorization: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json"
const url = new URL(
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/me"
);

const headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());

获取用户列表

requires authentication

Example request:
curl --request GET \
    --get "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/users?search=%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89&is_active=1&per_page=15" \
    --header "Authorization: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json"
const url = new URL(
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/users"
);

const params = {
    "search": "张三",
    "is_active": "1",
    "per_page": "15",
};
Object.keys(params)
    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

const headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());

Example response (401):

Show headers 
cache-control: no-cache, private
content-type: application/json
access-control-allow-origin: *
 

{
    "success": false,
    "code": 401,
    "message": "未授权，请先登录"
}
Received response:
Request failed with error:


Tip: Check that you're properly connected to the network.
If you're a maintainer of ths API, verify that your API is running and you've enabled CORS.
You can check the Dev Tools console for debugging information.

Request      

GET api/users

Headers

Authorization      

Example: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}

Content-Type      

Example: application/json

Accept      

Example: application/json

Query Parameters

search   string  optional  

搜索关键词（按用户名/邮箱/电话模糊匹配） Example: 张三

is_active   boolean  optional  

是否激活（1:激活, 0:未激活） Example: true

per_page   integer  optional  

每页数量 Example: 15

创建新用户

requires authentication

Example request:
curl --request POST \
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/users" \
    --header "Authorization: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json" \
    --data "{
    \"name\": \"张三\",
    \"email\": \"zhangsan@example.com\",
    \"password\": \"password123\",
    \"phone\": \"13800138000\",
    \"roles\": null
}"

const url = new URL(
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/users"
);

const headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "name": "张三",
    "email": "zhangsan@example.com",
    "password": "password123",
    "phone": "13800138000",
    "roles": null
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());
Received response:
Request failed with error:


Tip: Check that you're properly connected to the network.
If you're a maintainer of ths API, verify that your API is running and you've enabled CORS.
You can check the Dev Tools console for debugging information.

Request      

POST api/users

Headers

Authorization      

Example: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}

Content-Type      

Example: application/json

Accept      

Example: application/json

Body Parameters

name   string   

用户名 Example: 张三

email   string   

邮箱（唯一） Example: zhangsan@example.com

password   string   

密码（至少8位） Example: password123

phone   string  optional  

电话 Example: 13800138000

roles   string[]  optional  

角色ID数组
*   integer  optional  

角色ID（必须存在） Example: 1

更新用户信息

requires authentication

Example request:
curl --request PUT \
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/users/laboriosam" \
    --header "Authorization: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json" \
    --data "{
    \"name\": \"张三\",
    \"email\": \"zhangsan@example.com\",
    \"password\": \"newpassword123\",
    \"phone\": \"13800138000\",
    \"is_active\": true,
    \"roles\": null
}"

const url = new URL(
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/users/laboriosam"
);

const headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

);

const params = {
    "type": "order_status",
    "code": "pending",
    "label": "待处理",
    "is_active": "1",
    "group_by_type": "1",
    "per_page": "15",
};

    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

    "Authorization": "Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}",

    "Accept": "application/json",
};

    --header "Authorization: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json"
const url = new URL(
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/regions"
);

const params = {
    "parent_id": "1",
    "level": "省",
    "is_active": "1",
    "tree": "1",
    "per_page": "1000",
};
Object.keys(params)
    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

const headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());

创建新产品

requires authentication

Example request:
curl --request POST \
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/products" \
    --header "Authorization: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json" \
    --data "{
    \"category_id\": 1,
    \"name\": \"iPhone 15 Pro\",
    \"sku\": \"IPHONE15PRO001\",
    \"barcode\": \"1234567890123\",
    \"description\": \"最新款iPhone手机\",
    \"image\": \"https:\\/\\/example.com\\/image.jpg\",
    \"unit_id\": 1,
    \"purchase_price\": 8000,
    \"sale_price\": 9999,
    \"cost_price\": 7500,
    \"min_stock\": 10,
    \"max_stock\": 1000,
    \"is_active\": true
}"

const url = new URL(
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/products"
);

const headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "category_id": 1,
    "name": "iPhone 15 Pro",
    "sku": "IPHONE15PRO001",
    "barcode": "1234567890123",
    "description": "最新款iPhone手机",
    "image": "https:\/\/example.com\/image.jpg",
    "unit_id": 1,
    "purchase_price": 8000,
    "sale_price": 9999,
    "cost_price": 7500,
    "min_stock": 10,
    "max_stock": 1000,
    "is_active": true
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());

    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json"

    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/warehouse-locations"
);

    "warehouse_id": "1",
    "is_active": "1",
    "per_page": "1000",
};

Authorization      

Example: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}

Content-Type      

Example: application/json

Accept      

Example: application/json

Body Parameters

product_id   string   

The id of an existing record in the products table. Example: vel

from_warehouse_id   string   

产品ID（必填）. The id of an existing record in the warehouses table. Example: ipsa

to_warehouse_id   string   

源仓库ID（必填）. The id of an existing record in the warehouses table. Example: sapiente

from_location_id   string  optional  

目标仓库ID（必填）. The id of an existing record in the warehouse_locations table.

to_location_id   string  optional  

源库位ID. The id of an existing record in the warehouse_locations table.

quantity   integer   

目标库位ID. Must be at least 1. Example: 63

reference_no   string  optional  

调拨数量（必填）. Example: et

remark   string  optional  

关联单据号. Example: impedit

库存调整

requires authentication

Example request:
curl --request POST \
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/inventory/adjust" \
    --header "Authorization: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json" \
    --data "{
    \"product_id\": \"est\",
    \"warehouse_id\": \"distinctio\",
    \"quantity\": 89,
    \"unit_cost\": 62,
    \"reference_no\": \"alias\",
    \"remark\": \"iusto\"
}"

const url = new URL(
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/inventory/adjust"
);

const headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "product_id": "est",
    "warehouse_id": "distinctio",
    "quantity": 89,
    "unit_cost": 62,
    "reference_no": "alias",
    "remark": "iusto"
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());

获取供应商列表

requires authentication

Example request:
curl --request GET \
    --get "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/suppliers?search=%E5%8D%8E%E4%B8%BA&is_active=1&rating=A" \
    --header "Authorization: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json"
const url = new URL(
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/suppliers"
);

const params = {
    "search": "华为",
    "is_active": "1",
    "rating": "A",
};
Object.keys(params)
    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

const headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());

Headers

Content-Type      

Example: application/json

Accept      

Example: application/json

Query Parameters

search   string  optional  

搜索关键词 (按名称/编码/联系人/电话模糊匹配) Example: 华为

is_active   boolean  optional  

是否激活 (1:激活, 0:未激活) Example: true

rating   string  optional  

供应商评级 (A/B/C/D) Example: A

    \"is_active\": true,

}"

Request      

POST api/purchase-returns

Headers

Authorization      

Example: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}

Content-Type      

Example: application/json

Accept      

Example: application/json

Body Parameters

purchase_order_id   string  optional  

The id of an existing record in the purchase_orders table.

supplier_id   string   

关联采购订单ID（可选）. The id of an existing record in the suppliers table. Example: saepe

warehouse_id   string   

供应商ID（必填）. The id of an existing record in the warehouses table. Example: sequi

return_date   string   

仓库ID（必填）. Must be a valid date. Example: 2025-12-24T08:39:43

currency_id   string  optional  

退货日期（必填）. The id of an existing record in the currencies table.

remark   string  optional  

币种ID. Example: aut

items   object[]   

备注. Must have at least 1 items.
product_id   string   

退货明细（至少一条）. The id of an existing record in the products table. Example: nihil

quantity   integer   

产品ID. Must be at least 1. Example: 82

unit_price   number   

退货数量. Must be at least 0. Example: 19

tax_rate   number  optional  

单价. Must be at least 0. Must not be greater than 100. Example: 18

remark   string  optional  

税率. Example: consequatur

    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json"

    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/sales-orders"
);

const params = {
    "customer_id": "1",
    "warehouse_id": "1",
    "status": "approved",
    "start_date": "2024-01-01",
    "end_date": "2024-12-31",
    "search": "SO001",
    "per_page": "15",
};
Object.keys(params)
    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

const headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());

    --header "Authorization: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json" \
    --data "{
    \"customer_id\": \"cum\",
    \"warehouse_id\": \"cumque\",
    \"order_date\": \"2025-12-24T08:39:43\",
    \"delivery_date\": \"2025-12-24T08:39:43\",
    \"discount_amount\": 16,
    \"remark\": \"saepe\",
    \"items\": [
        {
            \"product_id\": \"maiores\",
            \"quantity\": 70,
            \"unit_price\": 6,
            \"tax_rate\": 11,
            \"discount_rate\": 7,
            \"remark\": \"inventore\"
        }
    ]
}"

const url = new URL(
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/sales-orders/sed"
);

const headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "customer_id": "cum",
    "warehouse_id": "cumque",
    "order_date": "2025-12-24T08:39:43",
    "delivery_date": "2025-12-24T08:39:43",
    "discount_amount": 16,
    "remark": "saepe",
    "items": [
        {
            "product_id": "maiores",
            "quantity": 70,
            "unit_price": 6,
            "tax_rate": 11,
            "discount_rate": 7,
            "remark": "inventore"
        }
    ]
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "PUT",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());

Request      

POST api/sales-settlements

Headers

Authorization      

Example: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}

Content-Type      

Example: application/json

Accept      

Example: application/json

Body Parameters

customer_id   string   

The id of an existing record in the customers table. Example: nemo

settlement_date   string   

客户ID（必填）. Must be a valid date. Example: 2025-12-24T08:39:43

currency_id   string  optional  

结算日期（必填）. The id of an existing record in the currencies table.

remark   string  optional  

币种ID（可选）. Example: quaerat

items   object[]   

备注（可选）. Must have at least 1 items.
reference_type   string   

结算明细（至少一条）. Example: sales_order

Must be one of:
  • sales_order
  • sales_return
reference_id   integer   

关联类型：销售订单或销售退货. Example: 2

remark   string  optional  

关联单据ID. Example: quod

获取BOM列表

requires authentication

Example request:
curl --request GET \
    --get "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/boms?product_id=1&is_active=1&is_default=1&search=V1.0&per_page=15" \
    --header "Authorization: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json"
const url = new URL(
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/boms"
);

const params = {
    "product_id": "1",
    "is_active": "1",
    "is_default": "1",
    "search": "V1.0",
    "per_page": "15",
};
Object.keys(params)
    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

const headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());

创建BOM

requires authentication

Example request:
curl --request POST \
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/boms" \
    --header "Authorization: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json" \
    --data "{
    \"product_id\": 1,
    \"version\": \"V1.0\",
    \"effective_date\": \"2024-01-01\",
    \"expiry_date\": \"2024-12-31\",
    \"is_default\": true,
    \"is_active\": true,
    \"description\": \"初始版本BOM\",
    \"items\": null
}"

const url = new URL(
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/boms"
);

const headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "product_id": 1,
    "version": "V1.0",
    "effective_date": "2024-01-01",
    "expiry_date": "2024-12-31",
    "is_default": true,
    "is_active": true,
    "description": "初始版本BOM",
    "items": null
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());
Received response:
Request failed with error:

POST api/boms

Headers

Authorization      

Example: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}

Content-Type      

Example: application/json

Accept      

Example: application/json

Body Parameters

product_id   integer   

产品ID Example: 1

version   string   

版本号 Example: V1.0

effective_date   date   

生效日期 Example: 2024-01-01

expiry_date   date  optional  

失效日期（必须晚于生效日期） Example: 2024-12-31

is_default   boolean  optional  

是否默认版本 Example: true

is_active   boolean  optional  

是否激活 Example: true

description   string  optional  

描述 Example: 初始版本BOM

items   string[]   

组件明细（至少一条）
component_product_id   string   

组件明细（至少一条）. The id of an existing record in the products table. Example: qui

quantity   number   

组件产品ID. Must be at least 0. Example: 15

unit_id   string  optional  

用量. The id of an existing record in the units table.

loss_rate   number  optional  

单位. Must be at least 0. Must not be greater than 100. Example: 17

sequence   integer  optional  

损耗率. Must be at least 0. Example: 73

position   string  optional  

序号. Must not be greater than 100 characters. Example: cyvuhqlzugmwyeevzhft

remark   string  optional  

位置. Example: id

*   object  optional  
component_product_id   integer   

组件产品ID Example: 2

quantity   number   

用量（最小0） Example: 2

unit_id   integer  optional  

单位ID Example: 1

loss_rate   number  optional  

损耗率（0-100） Example: 5

sequence   integer  optional  

序号 Example: 1

position   string  optional  

位置 Example: 主板

remark   string  optional  

备注 Example: 关键组件

获取工艺路线列表

requires authentication

Example request:
curl --request GET \
    --get "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/process-routes?product_id=1&is_active=1&is_default=1&search=V1.0&per_page=15" \
    --header "Authorization: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json"
const url = new URL(
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/process-routes"
);

const params = {
    "product_id": "1",
    "is_active": "1",
    "is_default": "1",
    "search": "V1.0",
    "per_page": "15",
};
Object.keys(params)
    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

const headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());

Example response (401):

创建工作流

requires authentication

Example request:
curl --request POST \
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/workflows" \
    --header "Authorization: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json" \
    --data "{
    \"name\": \"采购订单审批流程\",
    \"code\": \"PO_APPROVAL\",
    \"type\": \"purchase_order\",
    \"description\": \"采购订单审批流程\",
    \"is_active\": true,
    \"nodes\": null
}"

const url = new URL(
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/workflows"
);

const headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "name": "采购订单审批流程",
    "code": "PO_APPROVAL",
    "type": "purchase_order",
    "description": "采购订单审批流程",
    "is_active": true,
    "nodes": null
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());

是否激活 Example: true

nodes   string[]   

节点数组（至少一个）
node_name   string   

节点数组（至少一个）. Must not be greater than 255 characters. Example: uaddvswclmpwvfmekus

node_type   string   

节点名称. Example: end

Must be one of:
  • start
  • approval
  • condition
  • end
sequence   integer   

节点类型. Must be at least 1. Example: 33

approval_type   string  optional  

节点顺序. Example: single

Must be one of:
  • single
  • all
  • any
approver_config   object  optional  

审批类型.

condition_config   object  optional  

审批人配置.

next_nodes   object  optional  

条件配置.

timeout_hours   integer  optional  

下一节点. Must be at least 0. Example: 77

is_required   boolean  optional  

超时时间. Example: false

remark   string  optional  

是否必须. Example: cumque

条件配置

下一节点

);

const params = {
    "category": "sales",
    "is_active": "1",
    "per_page": "15",
};
Object.keys(params)
    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

const headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());

Example response (401):

Show headers 
cache-control: no-cache, private
content-type: application/json
access-control-allow-origin: *
 

{
    "success": false,
    "code": 401,
    "message": "未授权，请先登录"
}
Received response:
Request failed with error:

If you're a maintainer of ths API, verify that your API is running and you've enabled CORS.

创建自定义报表定义

requires authentication

Example request:
curl --request POST \
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/custom-reports" \
    --header "Authorization: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json" \
    --data "{
    \"name\": \"销售日报\",
    \"code\": \"SALES_DAILY\",
    \"category\": \"sales\",
    \"description\": \"每日销售统计报表\",
    \"query_config\": null,
    \"display_config\": null,
    \"is_active\": true
}"

const url = new URL(
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/custom-reports"
);

const headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "name": "销售日报",
    "code": "SALES_DAILY",
    "category": "sales",
    "description": "每日销售统计报表",
    "query_config": null,
    "display_config": null,
    "is_active": true
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());

Request      

GET api/notification-templates

Headers

Authorization      

Example: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}

Content-Type      

Example: application/json

Accept      

Example: application/json

Query Parameters

type   string  optional  

模板类型（system/approval/order/inventory/financial） Example: system

channel   string  optional  

发送渠道（system/email/sms/push） Example: email

is_active   boolean  optional  

是否激活（1:激活, 0:未激活） Example: true

per_page   integer  optional  

每页数量 Example: 15

创建通知模板

requires authentication

Example request:
curl --request POST \
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/notification-templates" \
    --header "Authorization: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json" \
    --data "{
    \"code\": \"order_approved\",
    \"name\": \"订单审批通过通知\",
    \"type\": \"order\",
    \"channel\": \"email\",
    \"subject\": \"订单审批通过\",
    \"content\": \"您的订单{{order_no}}已审批通过\",
    \"variables\": null,
    \"is_active\": true
}"

const url = new URL(
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/notification-templates"
);

const headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

let body = {
    "code": "order_approved",
    "name": "订单审批通过通知",
    "type": "order",
    "channel": "email",
    "subject": "订单审批通过",
    "content": "您的订单{{order_no}}已审批通过",
    "variables": null,
    "is_active": true
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body: JSON.stringify(body),
}).then(response => response.json());
Received response:
Request failed with error:

获取操作日志列表

requires authentication

Example request:
curl --request GET \
    --get "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/operation-logs?user_id=1&module=%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86&action=%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA&method=POST&status_code=200&search=%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7&date_from=2024-01-01&date_to=2024-12-31&per_page=15" \
    --header "Authorization: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json"
const url = new URL(
    "http://example-test.laravel.com/api/operation-logs"
);

const params = {
    "user_id": "1",
    "module": "用户管理",
    "action": "创建",
    "method": "POST",
    "status_code": "200",
    "search": "创建用户",
    "date_from": "2024-01-01",
    "date_to": "2024-12-31",
    "per_page": "15",
};
Object.keys(params)
    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

const headers = {
    "Authorization": "Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}",
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());

Example response (401):

Show headers 
cache-control: no-cache, private
content-type: application/json
access-control-allow-origin: *
 

{
    "success": false,
    "code": 401,
    "message": "未授权，请先登录"
}
Received response:
Request failed with error:

Request      

GET api/operation-logs

Headers

Authorization      

Example: Bearer Bearer {YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}

Content-Type      

Example: application/json

Accept      

Example: application/json

Query Parameters

user_id   integer  optional  

用户ID Example: 1

module   string  optional  

模块 Example: 用户管理

action   string  optional  

操作（模糊匹配） Example: 创建

method   string  optional  

HTTP请求方法（GET/POST/PUT/DELETE） Example: POST

status_code   integer  optional  

响应状态码 Example: 200

search   string  optional  

搜索关键词（按操作/路径/消息/用户名/邮箱模糊匹配） Example: 创建用户

date_from   string  optional  

date 开始日期 Example: 2024-01-01

date_to   string  optional  

date 结束日期 Example: 2024-12-31

per_page   integer  optional  

每页数量 Example: 15
